<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />Forgive me for shedding blood, God of my salvation,</para>

<para style="q1">and I will shout for the joy of your righteousness.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />Lord, open my lips,</para>

<para style="q1">and my mouth will express your praise.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />For you do not delight in sacrifice, or I would give it;</para>

<para style="q1">you have no pleasure in burnt offerings.</para>
